Description:
   Ninth Descent is an advanced Sentinel awareness technique named for the
   ninth and deepest level of the Pale Ledger's observational hierarchy. The
   Sentinel enters a heightened state of perceptual acuity, processing the
   flow of combat at an accelerated rate. For a brief window, the Sentinel
   can perceive openings and threats before they fully materialize.

   While active, Ninth Descent improves the Sentinel's dodge and parry rates
   significantly, as their enhanced perception allows them to anticipate
   attacks before they land. The technique also amplifies the damage of any
   counter-attacks made during this window, as the Sentinel can direct their
   responses to precisely targeted weak points. The heightened state is
   mentally taxing and cannot be sustained indefinitely.
